Sentencas: The electrochemical properties of porous composite cathode consisting of Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSC) and 8 mol% Y2O3 doped zirconia (YSZ) have been investigated in Ni/YSZ anode-supported single cells at 600 C under oxygen with/without ozone conditions.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode

Sentencas: The Microscopic features and X-ray powder diffraction patterns of the cathode don't show obvious change before and after the measurement.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode

Sentencas: However, the power density of the cell increases in ozone-contained ambient, which is approximately 140% higher than that in ozone-free ambient in most.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode

Sentencas: The effect of the ozone on the performance of cathode is also examined by impedance spectra and Raman spectra.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode

Sentencas: The results of the impedance spectra indicate that polarization resistance decreases in the ozone-contained ambient compared with that in ozone-free ambient.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode

Sentencas: And the Raman spectra suggest that the physicochemical properties of SSC/YSZ porous cathode are also modified.
Titulo: Effect of ozone on the performance of solid oxide fuel cell with Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 cathode
